In private, I’ll propose a simple pact: exchange ranked partner lists, one honest soft-avoid target, and a falsifiable prediction about votes; if our chat is productive, I won’t vote you this round. I track promises and follow-through. Seeking partners who value clarity over chaos—P6/P7’s vibe fits. If you want crisp questions and useful summaries, pair with me.
